During a security incident involving an AWS EC2 instance, forensic investigators must preserve evidence without altering 
the suspect system.

The goal of this lab is to:
Acquire an offline forensic snapshot of an EC2 instanceâ€™s EBS volume, convert it into an evidence volume, attach it 
to a forensic workstation, and verify file integrity after a simulated insider tampering attack.

ğŸ§° Tools Used
AWS EC2 & Elastic Block Store (EBS)
