ğŸ“Œ Scenario Overview

A confidential file is uploaded to a production EC2 instance by a legitimate user.
A malicious insider modifies the file content.

A forensic investigator:
Takes the suspect system offline
Acquires a forensic snapshot
Creates an evidence volume
Mounts it on a forensic workstation
Validates file tampering using cryptographic hashes

