ğŸ“š Lessons Learned
Cloud evidence must be acquired offline to preserve integrity
EBS snapshots act as forensic disk images in AWS
Evidence volumes allow safe analysis without contamination
Cryptographic hashes are essential for tampering detection
Forensic methodology applies equally to cloud environments
